msgid "%@; I’ll only pay for ads delivered up to cancellation."
msgstr "%@, e pagarei apenas pelos anúncios entregues até o cancelamento."

#. First part of checkbox text for accepting terms of service for the endless
#. Blaze campaign subscription. %1$.0f is the weekly budget amount, %2$@ is the
#. formatted start date. The content inside two double asterisks **...** denote
#. bolded text.
msgctxt "blazeCampaignCreationFormViewModel.tosCheckboxFirstLinePartEvergreen"
msgid "I agree to a recurring **weekly charge up to $%1$.0f** starting **%2$@**. Charges may occur at varying times during the campaign."
msgstr "Concordo com uma **cobrança semanal recorrente de até US$ %1$.0f**, começando em **%2$@**. As cobranças podem ocorrer em diferentes momentos durante a campanha."

#. First part of checkbox text for accepting terms of service for finite Blaze
#. campaigns with the duration up to 7 days. %1$.0f is the weekly budget
#. amount, %2$@ is the formatted start date. The content inside two double
#. asterisks **...** denote bolded text.
msgctxt "blazeCampaignCreationFormViewModel.tosCheckboxFirstLinePart.upToSevenDays"
msgid "I agree to be charged up to **$%1$.0f** starting **%2$@**. Charges may occur in one or more payments while the campaign is active."
msgstr "Concordo com a cobrança de até **US$ %1$.0f**, começando em **%2$@**. As cobranças podem ocorrer em um ou mais pagamentos enquanto a campanha está ativa."

#. First part of checkbox text for accepting terms of service for finite Blaze
#. campaigns with the duration of more than 7 days. %1$.0f is the weekly budget
#. amount, %2$@ is the formatted start date. The content inside two double
#. asterisks **...** denote bolded text.
msgctxt "blazeCampaignCreationFormViewModel.tosCheckboxFirstLinePart.MoreThanSevenDays"
msgid "I agree to a recurring charge of up to **$%1$.0f weekly** starting **%2$@**. Charges may occur at varying times during the campaign."
msgstr "Concordo com uma cobrança recorrente de até **US$ %1$.0f por semana** começando em **%2$@**. As cobranças podem ocorrer em diferentes momentos durante a campanha."

